                                                                We’re giving back together

                                                                8 December, 2016 | United Kingdom

                                                                Share

                                                                Share to FacebookThis link opens in a new window Share to TwitterThis link opens in a new window Share to Google+This link opens in a new window Email

                                                                Thanks to our riders and drivers in 65 cities and 31 countries who took part in UberGIVING. Together we made a difference—from volunteering at food banks in Portugal, to collecting toy donations in Kenya. We gave back to our cities and communities around the world.

                                                                It’s that time of year when we want to give back but it’s hard to know how. With UberGIVING we help you give back with the tap of a button.

                                                                Want to make a difference in your city?

                                                                It’s easy, here’s how you can take part in UberGIVING.

                                                                What: Donate

                                                                • Clothes
                                                                • Books
                                                                • Shoes
                                                                • Toys CDs/DVDs
                                                                • Household items
                                                                • Gifts, Jewellery, Ornaments and Handbags

                                                                When: 11am – 4pm on 10th December

                                                                Where: Belfast, Birmingham, Brighton, Bristol, Cambridge, Cardiff, Edinburgh, Glasgow, Leeds, Leicester, London, Manchester, Merseyside, Newcastle, Nottingham, Stoke, Southampton, Portsmouth, Sheffield, York and in cities across Europe, the Middle East and Africa.

                                                                How: Pickup service

                                                                More info: At the allotted time, simply request UberGIVING from inside the Uber app and a driver will come to your location to pick up your donation and take it to Age UK shops

                                                                In partnership with

                                                                 

                                                                Check out what else we’re doing for UberGIVING around the world

                                                                Discover UberGIVING

                                                                Only available between 11am – 4pm on Saturday 10 December 2016. There will be no charge to your account for requesting the UberGIVING service.

                                                                Posted by Sarah
